{"tid":612724,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"支付寶真係on99","createTime":"2018-04-01T05:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T06:55:15.000Z","uid":22898,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b674f68d7b055d7de8c5b6e0f3b595904ece67","tid":612724,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"去m記排隊用機買野食，前面排左一家人用緊，本身已經係一路簡一路㩒，用左部機好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等到佢比錢之後，佢又重新㩒過。我心諗：屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你買撚左部機呀！？我咪出聲講。<br />\n<br />\n個家人：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：又㩒過？你買左部機呀？<br />\n<br />\n佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢彈左出黎呀嘛，你估我想架？<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為係啲唔識用機既大陸人<br />\n<br />\n之後我睇住佢又重新操作一次，去到最後睇到佢用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支付寶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係又要揾scan位，又磨左幾秒。<br />\n<br />\n我終於明點解佢會咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 忍唔依講左句<br />\n「哦，原來係支付寶」<br />\n<br />\n佢走左之後，我以流暢既手法簡好個餐，拎出張八達通，一「嘟」，搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1ffba4c5f1371d41d603ca079f9489c6716b98","tid":612724,"uid":130479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:49:44.000Z","msg":"師兄好波"},{"pid":"df55fb4854763c6800fd4ca44fa231d270e4e6ed","tid":612724,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"713c7e08a90c09bd61d0112a264d37f5b216bd17","tid":612724,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:08:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a41488e80719f4e